Processing

Clean Column Names

points.df <- points.df %>%
    janitor::clean_names()

Count Race Number

points.df <- points.df %>%
    arrange(date) %>% 
    mutate(
        race_number = row_number()
    )

Long Form Dataset

points.df_long <- points.df %>% 
    dplyr::select(-mega_driver) %>% 
    tidyr::pivot_longer(
        cols      = !c(track, location, date, race_number), 
        names_to  = 'player',
        values_to = 'points'
        )

Cummulative Points

df_f1_cum <- points.df_long %>% 
    dplyr::arrange(date) %>% 
    dplyr::group_by(player) %>% 
    dplyr::mutate(
        points_cum = cumsum(points)
    )

Point Differential

df_f1_point_diff <- df_f1_cum %>% 
    group_by(race_number) %>% 
    mutate(
        max_points = max(points_cum),
        max_points_delta = points_cum - max_points
    )

Rank

df_f1_rank <- df_f1_cum %>% 
    dplyr::arrange(
        date, player, points_cum
    ) %>% 
    dplyr::group_by(
        date
    ) %>% 
    mutate(rank = rank(-points_cum, ties.method = 'min'))

# Assign names to colors
names(color_pal) <- players

Defined Shared Inputs

races <- df_f1_rank %>% 
    ungroup() %>%
    tidyr::drop_na() %>% 
    select(location) %>% 
    distinct() %>% 
    pull()

Create Dataset for Far Right Side Labels

df_name <- df_plot %>% 
    filter(
        race_number == max(df_plot$race_number)
    ) %>% 
    mutate(
        label = str_to_title(player)
    )

Generate Plot

p <- ggplot(
    data    = df_plot, 
    mapping = aes(
        x     = race_number,
        y     = rank,
        color = player,
        )
    ) +
    geom_point(size = 5) +
    geom_line(size = 2.5) +
    geom_label(
        data = df_name,
        mapping = aes(
            x = race_number, 
            y = rank, 
            label = label
        ),
        hjust = 0, 
        nudge_x = 0.5, 
        size = 13, 
        label.size = NA
        ) +
    scale_x_continuous(
        breaks = 1:max(df_plot$race_number),
        labels = races, 
        ) +
    scale_y_reverse(breaks = 1:7) +
    scale_color_manual(values = color_pal) +
    # scale_color_brewer(
    #     type = 'qual',
    #     palette = 'Dark2'
    #     ) +
    labs(
        title = 'F1 Fantasy Ranking By Race', 
        x = '',
        y = ''
    ) +
    coord_cartesian(clip = 'off') +
    theme_classic() +
    theme(
        axis.line = element_line(size = 1.5),
        axis.text.x = element_text(
            hjust = 1,
            angle = 45, 
            size = 25
            ),
        axis.text.y = element_text(
            hjust = 0,
            size = 35,
        ),
        axis.ticks = element_blank(),
        legend.position="none", 
        plot.margin = margin(
            t = 0, r = 100, b = 0, l = 0, 
            unit = "pt"
            ),
        plot.title = element_text(
            hjust = 0,
            size = 40
            )
        )

p

Save

filename_prefix = 'f1_fantasy_rank'

# Define File Name
race_location <- df_plot %>% 
    tail(1) %>% 
    pull(location)

race_date <- df_plot %>% 
    tail(1) %>% 
    pull(date)
    
file_name_wo_ext <- paste(
    filename_prefix,
    race_date,
    race_location,
    sep = '_'
    )

file_name_wo_ext <- gsub(" ", "-", file_name_wo_ext)

file_name <- paste(
    file_name_wo_ext,
    '.png',
    sep = ''
)

# Save copy with race specific name
ggsave(
  filename = file_name,
  plot     = p,
  device   = 'png',
  path     = './../data/plots',
  scale = 1,
  width = 16.2,
  height = 10,
  units = "in",
  dpi = 300,
  limitsize = TRUE
)

# Save general copy

Generate Plot

p <- ggplot(
    data    = df_plot, 
    mapping = aes(
        x     = race_number,
        y     = max_points_delta,
        color = player,
        )
    ) +
    geom_point(size = 5) +
    geom_line(size = 2.5, ) +
    ggrepel::geom_text_repel(
        data = df_name,
        mapping = aes(
            x = race_number, 
            y = max_points_delta, 
            label = label
        ),
        hjust = 0, 
        nudge_x = 01,
        size = 13, 
        segment.color = NA,
        direction = "y"
        ) +
    scale_x_continuous(
        breaks = 1:max(df_plot$race_number),
        labels = races, 
        limits = c(1, length(races) + 4)
        ) +
    scale_color_manual(values = color_pal) +
    labs(
        title = 'F1 Fantasy Point Differential To Leader', 
        x = '',
        y = ''
    ) +
    theme_classic() +
    theme(
        axis.line = element_line(size = 1.5),
        axis.text.x = element_text(
            hjust = 1,
            angle = 45, 
            size = 25
            ),
        axis.text.y = element_text(
            hjust = 0,
            size = 35,
        ),
        axis.ticks = element_blank(),
        legend.position="none", 
        plot.margin = margin(
            t = 0, r = 0, b = 0, l = 0, 
            unit = "pt"
            ),
        plot.title = element_text(
            hjust = 0,
            size = 40
            )
        )
